description:
Try To Go To The FireWall

A Game Made for the Trijam #188 in 3h.

It's a game where you need to go to the FireWall, but not in a common way. You will need to sabotage the GamePlay to have more Speed, ForceJump, or even change location of things.

Kapris Dimitri
